  <!-- EN: A stack of antipersonnel plasma pulse grenades. The resulting explosion will ignite anything nearby. -->
  <RM_Weapon_GrenadePlasmaImmolator.description>一叠杀伤人员等离子脉冲榴弹。爆炸会点燃附近的任何东西。</RM_Weapon_GrenadePlasmaImmolator.description>
